\int_0^{\infty}\frac{\ln y}{y^2+1}\mathrm{dy}=0
\int_0^{\infty}\frac{\ln x}{x^2+a^2}\mathrm{dx}=\frac{\ln a}{a}\int_0^{\infty}\frac{1}{y^2+1}\mathrm{dy}+\frac{1}{a}\int_0^{\infty}\frac{\ln y}{y^2+1}\mathrm{dy}=\frac{\pi\ln a}{2a}
